{
  "stem": "1929.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would call me Jew and things, even if I was the son--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Definitely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The son's owner, they didn't--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was really scared of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That would be the very, very first memories, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was to-- I used to go to school, at that time, I was going to first grade, I guess, or second grade.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Something like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would be throwing stones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There would be a bunch of kids.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would gather up on the corner and they would throw stones, and they would call me names.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Dirty Jew, and things like that, in Polish, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I just couldn't understand why they were doing that, because I kind of admired them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to be part of the hooligans, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- They wouldn't let you become part of their gang?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would just beat me up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they sent-- from then on, somebody was escorting me to the-- to school usually.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think the maid came with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to cover my, my face up with my hands so they wouldn't see that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I got very quickly, I was wondering why, and I got the idea that, that it was about being Jewish that made me bad, different, evil.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what-- that's why they were doing what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't understand it at the time, but I got-- I got the connection that being Jewish meant that you were being hated.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's very early in life, I got that message.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That being Jewish was not something desirable to be, because that automatically puts you in danger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Other people would despise you and be violent against you.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
